Sensor data quality issues refer to any data points with quality scores below a certain threshold or any other predefined criteria; 
 Sensors are considered to be experiencing data quality issues if they have a certain number of issues within a specific time frame (in this case, the year 2023); 
 This query can be used to identify sensors that require maintenance or calibration to improve data quality.

sql:
SELECT MAX(timestamp)
FROM sensor_data
WHERE sensor_id = 1;
